<li>Transfer time: approx. 3hrs 15mins by rail from Zurich airport or 3hrs 30mins by rail from Geneva airport. Your journey may involve two or three changes of train, depending on the train you catch.</li>
<li>150 metres to the nearest bus stop</li>
<li>Just 300 metres from the Eiger Express, Cog Railway, and Männlichen Gondola</li>
<li>5 minutes by bus to the town centre</li>
<li>Grill and pizzeria within easy walking distance</li>
</ul>]]></locationDescription>
