  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Doubles</strong> sleep two people with an Austrian twin bed and have a modern and clean décor. </p>
<p><strong>South-Facing Doubles</strong> are similar in size and style to standard doubles with an Austrian twin bed. They also have a balcony and south-facing view.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong> sleep three to four people. They an Austrian twin bed and additional bunk beds.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in time: <strong>3pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out time: <strong>11am</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A local tourist tax of approx. CHF 5.25 per person per night is payable locally (children aged 12-15 years pay a reduced rate of CHF 4.75 per person per night, and guests aged 12 and under are exempt).</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
